items.badge_description: Water, barley, yeast, and hops - such simple ingredients to produce such a marvelous concoction! Let's raise a toast to your favorite beverage on this National Beer Day!
After a long day, what better way to kick back than with a crisp and refreshing lager? You're already feeling more relaxed, aren't you?. That's 85 different Lagers! Try 5 more to unlock Level 18.
